Monica Geller: I just thought that if I could follow the wire I could find out what it did .

Rachel Green: And did you ?!

Monica Geller: No . It disappears back there behind that baseboard . For a minute there , I thought it went downstairs .

#NOTE#: ( Rachel removes a paper on the floor which is covering a hole and gasps . )

Monica Geller: But it did n't . Say hello to Mrs. Chatracus .

Rachel Green: Oh my God .

Mrs. Chatracus: Hello darling .

Rachel Green: Hello , Mrs. Chatracus .
